</p>
<p>establishment and the Army of the United States of America to refer to a set of principles contained in 
the Field Manual on Counterinsurgency (Field Manual (FM) 3-24). See, inter alia, Gian P. Gentile, 
&#8220;Time for the deconstruction of Field Manual 3-24&#8221;, <i>Joint Force Quarterly</i>, No. 58 (third quarter 
