</p>
<p><i>guardian.co.uk</i>, March 2011. Available from 
www.guardian.co.uk/world/datablog/2011/mar/28/afghanistan-civilian-compensation. 
</p>
<p> 43 See A/HRC/11/2/Add.4, paras. 38-43. 
 44 See Amnesty International, &#8220;Afghanistan: Taleban must immediately stop targeting civilians in 
</p>
